GMS Unlock LSPosed contains a standalone adaptation of the GMS unlock
hook from REAREye.

Original project:
https://github.com/killerprojecte/REAREye

Original file:
app/src/main/java/hk/uwu/reareye/hook/scopes/system/modules/misc/GMSUnlockModule.kt

The adapted hook keeps the same behavior: remove these Android system
feature flags from com.android.server.SystemConfig:

- cn.google.services
- com.google.android.feature.services_updater

